阿姨是为了真切体会师傅们的工作。 2023年8月，黄女士发文称，在7月份北大食堂工作正式满一年，十年前自己去长沙读书，后一路考到北京的学校读新闻传播专业，后来又成功保研北大。十年后，她找到了人生的新方向、新事业，“先从食堂阿姨一步步做起！” 26岁北大研究生当食堂阿姨：不用脑力劳动，比互联网大厂更快乐，想做食堂经理"},"attached_info":"CkoIuKXx/J+/l6BmEAMaCTExNDIwOTY2MCDp1Ze/BjAAOIkBQAtyEzE4ODg4Njc2MDE4MjE3MjU4Mjl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"162 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-643e9c15aaf37928640f192b0e0baa60_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"12_1743219130.635468","card_id":"Q_15691958794","target":{"id":15691958794,"title":"清朝为什么不认金朝祖宗，反而把宋朝视为正统延续？请进了帝王庙?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/15691958794","type":"question","created":1742857576,"answer_count":31,"follower_count":107,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"为什么清朝不认金朝为祖宗，反而把宋朝视为正统？其实正统这种传承机制，完全是可以灵活操作的，规矩嘛人定的！ 清朝也不是说一开始就认宋朝是正统的延续。相反，清朝在最初几乎是把所有出名的游牧民族皇帝，全部都给请进了中国历代帝王庙。"},"attached_info":"CkEIuKXx/J+/l6BmEAMaCTExNDE1NjkyNSDoyoe/BjAAOGtADHILMTU2OTE5NTg3OTR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"161 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-4509d68a72aab5572c429f96f8d45268_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"13_1743219130.636005","card_id":"Q_15619645902","target":{"id":15619645902,"title":"王兴兴最新发声「今年的需求点爆了，不光是宇树科技」，机器人行业发展现状如何？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/15619645902","type":"question","created":1742728218,"answer_count":35,"follower_count":94,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[349,395,1740,105508],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"3月23日上午，由国务院发展研究中心主办、中国发展研究基金会承办的中国发展高层论坛2025年年